main event: An unidentified flying object was observed moving from NNW to SSE with a stop and go motion, reversing direction and fading out.
interesting points: The sighting occurred on 31 August 1963 in Seattle, Washington., The observation type was classified as ground-visual., The sighting is considered questionable and unresolved due to insufficient data., The report is part of the Project Blue Book investigations into UFOs., No photographs were available as part of the report.
